1. **Treća** osoba jednine je teška za upotrebu. (The third person singular is difficult to use.)
2. Imam samo **treću** šansu da to popravim. (I only have a third chance to fix it.)
3. Ona je **treća** u nizu naslednika. (She is the third in line of inheritance.)
4. Moram da dovršim **treću** lekciju iz matematike. (I have to finish the third math lesson.)
5. **Trećom** godinom fakulteta počinjemo da učimo praktične veštine. (In the third year of college, we start learning practical skills.)
6. **Treću** nedelju zaredom idemo na istu plažu. (We are going to the same beach for the third week in a row.)
7. **Treću** godinu zaredom, naš tim osvaja prvo mesto. (For the third year in a row, our team is winning the first place.)
8. Njih dvoje su **treći** par koji se razvodi ove godine. (They are the third couple that is getting divorced this year.)
9. **Trećim** kvartalom očekujemo rast prodaje. (We expect sales growth in the third quarter.)
10. Nisam siguran da li bih **treću** čokoladu smeo da pojedem. (I'm not sure if I dare to eat the third chocolate.)

(Note: I used bold to highlight the word "treća" instead of a star.)